System bach nrja3 tree of choices b tari9a tkon more automated , JSON type of shit imkn 

Turn this from


Effect disponible 
Healing Effect:
"effect": {
    "heal": 20  // Heals the player for 20 HP
}

Attack Buff :
"effect": {
    "buff_attack": 5  // Increases player's attack by 5
}

Defense Buff :
"effect": {
    "buff_defense": 3  // Increases player's defense by 3
}

Damage Effect:
"effect": {
    "damage": 10  // Deals 10 damage to the player
}

You can combine multiple effects:

"effect": {
    "heal": 20,
    "buff_attack": 5,
    "buff_defense": 3
}